        <div class="nd-panel" data-section="sugar">
            <div class="nd-panel-header">
                <span class="nd-panel-tag">Divisions</span>
                <h2>Sugar, Cogen &amp; Bio-chemicals Business</h2>
            </div>

            <!-- Division Banner Image -->
            <div class="div-banner">
                <img src="~/images/Divisions/sugar.jpg" alt="Sugar, Cogen & Bio-chemicals" class="div-banner-img" />
            </div>

            <div class="comp-body">

                <p>Over the last seven decades, TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd. has grown to become one of the most trusted names in the field of sugar plant and machinery. The manufacturing unit in Pune was set up in 1957 and since then the company has served the sugar industry as the most trusted technology partner all along the various phases and challenges the sugar industry has faced over the years.</p>

                <p>TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd. is one of the original equipment manufacturers of sugar plant machinery and have successfully supplied and commissioned plants of varied capacities ranging from 800 TCD to 18,000 TCD and have capability to design as well as supply sugar plant up to 20,000 TCD.</p>

                <p>We have a proven track record for supplying turnkey sugar and cogeneration power plants and have till date successfully supplied and commissioned over 135 sugar plants with major expansions including more than 550 sugar cane mills, more than 5400 batch and continuous centrifugal machines and more than 200 boilers.</p>

                <p>TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd. went global in the year 1975 after supplying a 3500 TCD sugar plant expandable to 6000 TCD along with the sugar refinery to Malaysia. Ever since, TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd. has exported full plants and other major equipment to more than 35 countries including Algeria, Australia, Austria, Bangladesh, Burundi, Czech Republic, El-Salvador, Ecuador, Ethiopia, Fiji, Germany, Greece, Indonesia, India, Iran, Kenya, Mauritius, Malaysia, Malawi, Myanmar, Nigeria, Nepal, Pakistan, Poland, Philippines, Rwanda, Russia, Spain, Senegal, Sudan, Thailand, Uganda, Ukraine, Vietnam, Zambia. The fact that the company has exported large number of Batch &amp; Continuous Centrifugal machines to European market, meeting stringent quality norms and also competing with established European manufacturers, which is a testimony to the success of the company in export business all over the globe.</p>

                <p>TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd. has a proud tradition of innovation and ever since its inception has consistently brought state-of-the-art solutions to the Sugar industry with steady innovations and new sophisticated cutting edge technologies. We have developed and supplied large number of highly efficient falling film evaporators, continuous vacuum pans for improved steam economy, batch centrifugal machines from 750 kg/charge to 2250 kg/charge and continuous centrifugal machines of 1100 mm and 1500 mm diameter respectively. We have also developed 2-Roller mill having unique features combining advantages of power saving, lower bagasse moisture as well as higher pol extraction.</p>

                <p>To cater to the trend of higher capacity sugar plants, TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd. introduced the largest capacity equipment viz. 2-Roller mill of 1440 mm × 2800 mm (55 inch × 110 inch) size, batch centrifugal machine of 2250 kg/charge and falling film evaporator of 7000 sq. m heating surface.</p>

                <p>TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd. is also credited for engineering skills par excellence, for up gradation, modernization and expansion of the sugar plants and over the years have worked closely with many of the sugar factories to enhance their capacities and performance. Our company is well known for their project management skills and helped the investors by offering complete plants on turn-key basis including civil works. Timely delivery, execution and erection of the projects and also after sales service have always been strengths of the company.</p>

                <p>TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd. is equipped with the most modern, highly developed industrial manufacturing amenities at Pune as well as at Hyderabad and are supported by a group of service facilities.</p>

                <p>To cater to the needs of customers through a single window, TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd. have a dedicated team for customer solutions to offer services from concept stage to feasibility study, bankable detailed project report, cane development, process selection, operation support, maintenance support, etc.</p>

            </div>
        </div>

