                <div class="comp-body">
                    <p>TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd., has built cement plants that are fuel and energy efficient and also environment friendly. Its sustained success in winning repeated new orders has established it as one of the leading cement plant making companies in India. TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd. has designed, manufactured, supplied, installed and commissioned large capacity sophisticated cement plants for more than three decades in association with thyssenkrupp Polysius GmbH (tk Polysius), Germany.</p>

                    <p>tk Polysius is one of the world's leading engineering firms specializing in plant and equipment for the cement and mineral processing industry. tk Polysius plant and equipment with a brand name "POLYSIUS" are at the forefront of the technology and are available for comminution, pyro-processing, material handling and automation.</p>

                    <p>The efficient production of high grade cement products demands far more than combining individual machines or even ideal partial process steps. The required success can only be achieved by considering the entire production process and optimizing it as a whole, taking due account of capital cost and operating expenses.</p>

                    <p>For this reason, tk Polysius systematically consolidates process and plant knowhow to create innovative concepts for the process sectors of raw material preparation, clinker manufacturing and cement manufacturing, which are in turn incorporated into economical overall solutions for the complete cement production process.</p>

                    <p>As one of the world's leading companies in the plant engineering field, tk Polysius has the comprehensive know-how that is needed in order to supply the mining, metallurgical, refractories, lime and chemical industries with innovative but tried and tested processes, plants and system configurations. Repeatedly, tk Polysius has been successful in producing convincing solutions for pyro-processing and grinding applications, proving itself a reliable partner in all regions of the world.</p>

                    <p>Increasing the size of production units and improving the operating economy of production plants by reducing their power requirement and boosting their availability are main development priorities. tk Polysius has taken on these challenges and is pushing back the technological frontiers through specifically directed research and development strategies.</p>

                    <p>We have supplied and successfully commissioned several integrated cement plants of capacities ranging from 650 to 10,000 tons per day in India and overseas. In addition, split location clinker grinding units and various equipment and machinery have also been supplied by us. Cement plants with modern and up-to-date technology from tk Polysius are in operation across the length and breadth of India, running at more than their rated capacities and are distinct on account of their sustained efficiency and output levels.</p>

                    <p>Our references include the star performers in the Indian Cement Industry like Ambuja Cements and ACC Ltd. (Adani group), UltraTech Cement (Aditya Birla group), The India Cements Ltd. (ICL group), Vasavadatta Cement and Mangalam Cement (B.K. Birla group), Jaiprakash Associates Ltd. (Jaypee group), JK Cement, Birla Corporation, Wonder Cement, Penna Cement, Dalmia Cement, Trumboo Cement, Shree Cement, Star Cement (Meghalaya), etc. Overseas projects include projects in Bharain, Bangladesh, Benin, Cameroon, Cote D'Ivoire, Ghana, Indonesia, Kenya, Liberia, Malawi, Mali, Mozambique, Nepal, South Africa, Sri Lanka, Sudan, Togo, UAE and Uganda.</p>
                </div>
