            <div class="comp-body">

                <p>Established in 1976, TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd. Energy division has been one of the prime business verticals of TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd.</p>

                <p>TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd. been in the business of large capacity boilers since 1970s, making its beginning by developing boilers for the Sugar industry. The Boiler and Power Plant division grew up to become one of company's prime business verticals and today offers complete turnkey solutions for thermal power plants.</p>

                <p>The offerings include tried and tested boiler technologies for a wide variety of solid, liquid and gaseous fuels along with waste heat recovery (WHR)/ HRSG Systems. The state of the art manufacturing facilities at Pune and Hyderabad assist in manufacturing some of the most critical and key boiler components and thus we ensure that the quality of steam generators manufactured by TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd. is nothing but just perfect!</p>

                <h3>Our Key Products &amp; Range includes:</h3>
                <ul class="div-list">
                    <li>Circulating Fluidized Bed Combustion (CFBC) boilers for a variety of fuels (Also available in multiples of single units of 300 MWe)</li>
                    <li>Biomass boilers (up to 250 TPH)</li>
                    <li>Oil &amp; Gas fired boilers (up to 300 TPH)</li>
                    <li>Waste Heat Recovery boilers (up to 500 TPH)</li>
                    <li>HRSGs (suitable up to frame size 9FA)</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="div-footnote">*TPH – Tons of steam production per hour</p>

                <h3>Key References:</h3>
                <ul class="div-list">
                    <li>More than 250 references in India and Overseas for power generation and combined Heat and Power (Co-generation) applications for a variety of industries.</li>
                </ul>

                <p>Boiler and Power Plant has well established itself in the field of engineering, design, manufacture, supply, installation and commissioning of a wide range of steam and power generation unit's plants for various industrial and utility applications. Boiler package offerings, BTG offerings and turnkey power plant offerings are available.</p>

                <p>The experienced and qualified team of power professionals headed by a competent and senior management team of energy professionals from the industry, has been the key driver for Boiler and Power Plant's success and makes us one of India's most trusted brand for Boilers &amp; Power Plants.</p>

            </div>
