                <div class="comp-body">

                    <h3>Asset Management</h3>

                    <p>Our Asset Management (operation and maintenance) service is a customized solution which we provide to our customers as per their specific business requirements. With this solution, we unlock the untapped value through better performance, life enhancement and O&amp;M cost optimization. We can also offer spare parts, maintenance consumables, over hauls and third part services etc as a part of these services.</p>

                    <p>Our engagement with customer starts with initial meeting with customer to define / understand their requirement on scope of work and responsibility distribution. It is followed by plant visit and technical discussions, after technical alignment and KPIs finalisation, commercial discussions are concluded followed by the conclusion of contract.</p>

                    <p>In these contracts, TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd. takes over the full responsibility for the plant and ensures committed output by implementing its asset management system covering 7 dimensions:</p>

                    <ul class="div-list">
                        <li>Health, safety, environment and statutory management</li>
                        <li>Operations management</li>
                        <li>Maintenance management</li>
                        <li>Materials and services management</li>
                        <li>Performance improvement</li>
                        <li>Management information system (MIS) and visibility</li>
                        <li>People management</li>
                    </ul>

                    <p>TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd. has experience in operation and maintenance in wide range of industries including captive power plants, mining systems, coal handling plants, waste heat recovery power plant, cement plant and dry bulk cargo handling system at port.</p>

                    <p>The key advantages for customers are service advantages:</p>

                    <ul class="div-list">
                        <li>Tailor made solution to cater to customer's specific requirement</li>
                        <li>Better performance and longer life at optimum costs</li>
                        <li>Improved safety, reliability, availability, productivity, life and efficiency of physical assets</li>
                        <li>Leverage of our engineering knowhow in operation and maintenance</li>
                        <li>World class operation and maintenance practices</li>
                    </ul>

                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ── Parts Supply & Management ── -->
            <div class="cement-panel" id="svc-parts">
                <div class="comp-body">

                    <h3>Parts Supply &amp; Management</h3>

                    <p>Timely availability of genuine and quality spare parts is essential for an operating plant's uptime, productivity &amp; performance.</p>
                    <p>At TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd., we strive to proactively ensure availability of the apt spares at customers' plants at all times.</p>
                    <p>We are also focussed on innovative solutions aimed at reducing downtimes and improving plant performance. Spare parts are a crucial component of this endeavour.</p>
                    <p>With years of experience with inspections, evaluations, troubleshooting, our specialists closely study the equipment and parts behaviour under actual duty conditions and develop enhanced propositions, harnessing latest technological developments, which are also imbibed in the spare parts supplied for already supplied equipment, from time to time. This enables the existing operating equipment to derive benefits from the continuous product improvement program.</p>
                    <p>The parts supply and management segment caters to equipment in cement plants, boilers and power plants, open cast mining and bulk material handling and sugar plants.</p>
                    <!-- Image Carousel -->
